# FrankenFS Support-State Accounting

- Version: `bd-mpcse-support-state-accounting-v1`
- Rows: `13`
- Flat parity rejected: `true`
- Release gate contract: bd-rchk0.5.6.1 fail-closed release evaluator consumes support-state rows
- Reproduction: `ffs-harness validate-support-state-accounting --issues .beads/issues.jsonl --feature-parity FEATURE_PARITY.md --out artifacts/parity/support_state_accounting.json --summary-out artifacts/parity/support_state_accounting.md`

